export const TriIcon = () => {
  return (
    <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      width="17.176"
      height="38.706"
      viewBox="0 0 17.176 38.706"
    >
      <defs>
        <filter
          id="Polygone_1"
          x="0"
          y="0.415"
          width="17.176"
          height="38.291"
          filterUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
        >
          <feOffset dy="3" input="SourceAlpha" />
          <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="3" result="blur" />
          <feFlood floodOpacity="0.122" />
          <feComposite operator="in" in2="blur" />
          <feComposite in="SourceGraphic" />
        </filter>
      </defs>
      <g id="triangle" transform="translate(-366.327 -315.958)">
        <g
          transform="matrix(1, 0, 0, 1, 366.33, 315.96)"
          filter="url(#Polygone_1)"
        >
          <path
            id="Polygone_1-2"
            data-name="Polygone 1"
            d="M10,0,20,16.83H0Z"
            transform="matrix(-0.02, -1, 1, -0.02, 9.35, 26.71)"
            fill="#fff"
          />
        </g>
        <path
          id="Tracé_8"
          data-name="Tracé 8"
          d="M1930,393.473V373.618l4.328-8.176v34.649Z"
          transform="translate(-1542 -49.484)"
          fill="#fff"
        />
      </g>
    </svg>
  );
};
